th:900px; margin: 1.2rem 0;\"\u003e\r\n  \u003ciframe width=\"100%\" height=\"250\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ebeWruZ1ozk\" title=\"Polygatari-Matsuri\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen\u003e\u003c/iframe\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e","description":"試著嘗試使用更多色彩的作品。","image":null,"permalink":"http://localhost:1313/composition/atarayo/","title":"あたらよ(Atarayo)"},{"content":"\u003cdiv class=\"youtube-embed\" style=\"max-width:900px; margin: 1.2rem 0;\"\u003e\r\n  \u003ciframe width=\"100%\" height=\"250\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/avDgWoLj_Ao\" title=\"2-25\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen\u003e\u003c/iframe\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eA short piece written for recorder quintet, imitating the lively atmosphere of Chinese New Year.\nBlending fantasy and folk-ish styles, it features strong rhythmic patterns and non-functional harmonies to evoke a sense of Eastern mystery and celebration.\u003c/p\u003e","description":"我的木笛四重奏作品，嘗試融合奇幻、民俗風格。","image":null,"permalink":"http://localhost:1313/composition/2-25/","title":"2-25"},{"content":"\u003cdiv class=\"youtube-embed\" style=\"max-width:900px; margin: 1.2rem 0;\"\u003e\r\n  \u003ciframe width=\"100%\" height=\"250\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/mwNRsrCOfXo\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen\u003e\u003c/iframe\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e","description":"試著挑戰聽眾對於”相對剝奪感“的感受","image":null,"permalink":"http://localhost:1313/composition/relative_deprivation/","title":"相對剝奪感 Relative Deprivation"},{"content":"\u003cdiv class=\"youtube-embed\" style=\"max-width:900px; margin: 1.2rem 0;\"\u003e\r\n  \u003ciframe width=\"100%\" height=\"250\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/fXnTvqZvXmY\" title=\"Pol